      <p>
        I wish to present this project in two main parts: (1) a web-app, which may be self-hosted or embedded onto an Akademie Schloss Solitude webpage; and (2) an essay, which contextualizes the project at the intersection of post-war European sound art, cybernetics and machine learning, and the metaphysics of attention. Additionally, I will be living in Berlin in August and September of this year, and would enjoy leading performances/happenings in Germany using this project.
